    75тЖТ##### CMD
    76тЖТ
    77тЖТOn Windows the environment variable is set using the `set` command.
    78тЖТ
    79тЖТ```cmd
    80тЖТset DEBUG=*,-not_this
    81тЖТ```
    82тЖТ
    83тЖТExample:
    84тЖТ
    85тЖТ```cmd
    86тЖТset DEBUG=* & node app.js
    87тЖТ```
